A member of the House of Representatives from Rivers State, Hon. Farah Dagogo, has cautioned against the implementation of the Kaduna State Governor, Mallam Nasir el-Rufai-led All Progressives Congress (APC) Committee Report, with respect to true federalism.  THE Ijaw Youth Council, IYC,  worldwide has called on the Federal Government to take steps to implement the core recommendations of the ruling All Progressives Congress, APC, Committee’s report on restructuring, power devolution and true federalism. July 9, 2018 In "News" YENAGOA THE Ijaw Youth Council (IYC)  worldwide has called on the Federal Government to commence the steps to implement the core recommendations of the ruling All Progressives Congress, APC, Committee’s report on restructuring, power devolution and true federalism. July 9, 2018 In "News" Governor Henry Seriake Dickson of Bayelsa State has commended the ruling All Progressive Congress APC, on its far reaching recommendations on the issue of the proposed restructuring of the country. January 27, 2018 In "News"